  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Although Computed tomography (CT) is not routinely used to evaluate beast masses, It is
      common to discover Incidental breast lesions on chest CT.

      The goal of this study is to investigate the incidence and appearance of incidentally
      discovered breast masses on chest CT.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
